By Kevin Thomas 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Mr. Rock and Roll (AMC Wednesday at 3 a.m.), a dramatized 1957 account of how 
deejay Alan Freed discovered rock 'n' roll, features a roster of '50s rockers. 
</P>
