</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 AND ONE MORE THING: Austrian forces are making moves into territory held by 
the Spanish.Don't panic. It's not the start of World War III -- just the latest 
move in the Chant Wars. 
</P>
<P>
 With record companies searching high and low to cash in on the chantmania 
started by the success of "Chant," an album by Spain's Benedictine Monks of 
Santo Domingo de Silos, the newest entry is "Mystical Chants" by the Choir of 
Vienna, which has entered the Billboard Top 200 album chart. 
</P>
<P>
 What next? A hit collection of Swiss yodels? 
</P>
