<P>
 * * Gilby Clarke, "Pawn Shop Guitars," Virgin. Guns N' Roses guitarist Clarke 
and his friends add nothing to the retro hard-rock formula.The cast includes 
bandmates Slash and Axl Rose -- who duets on the Rolling Stones' "Dead 
Flowers." While neither Clarke's voice nor the songs are exceptional, the album 
possesses a heartfelt, bar-band quality that makes for agreeable ear candy. 
</P>
