members of Jane's Addiction marks both the band's birth and demise -- guitarist 
Dave Navarro has defected to the Red Hot Chili Peppers.Pity, because the canny 
lyrics and apocalyptic musicality create compelling soundscapes. Though the 
overall thrust is a bit meandering, the album is ultimately engrossing. 
