<HEADLINE>
<P>
LEAVING L.A. 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 * Bye-bye, Los Angeles . . . it's time for me to pack up and move out. After 
living here for 43 years, I find that my senses are transmitting "Mayday!" . . 
. the result of too many guys wearing earrings and too many girls wearing 
tattoos. 
</P>
<P>
 MICHAEL LUDMER 
</P>
<P>
 Encino 
</P>
</TEXT>
