<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA073194-0408 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 065927 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
July 31, 1994, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Real Estate; Part K; Page 6; Column 1; Real Estate Desk 
</P>
